    "body" : "<p>Here's one <a href=\"http://marxsoftware.blogspot.com/p/my-publications.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">view</a> on the singleton methods:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>I have found these various \"singleton\" methods to be useful for passing a single value to an API that requires a collection of that value. Of course, this works best when the code processing the passed-in value does not need to add to the collection.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
